            <title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Adds a 5-letter &apos;<link linkend="d4/dff/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_code">Code</link>&apos; field to the extended model and makes it readonly in CMS, and adds ability for a code of SYSTM to be filtered out via augmentSQL extension call. </para>
